{"tid":2107870,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★惠康全線指定貨品限購2件　包括大米雞蛋廁紙","createTime":"2020-07-14T07:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-14T07:59:16.000Z","uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"2f425f51d908159dcfaf4e213a8367fc15b7b917","tid":2107870,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-14T07:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200714/359719942221860864.jpeg/B11KeW1LIw3usGIKs49NFdjiJ27YWjPpD-dzYQ_nc2E?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200714%2F359719942221860864.jpeg%2FB11KeW1LIw3usGIKs49NFdjiJ27YWjPpD-dzYQ_nc2E%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=7ffb2c03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n本港新冠肺炎疫情反彈，政府再次收緊防疫措施，明天（15日）零時起禁止食肆每日下午6時至翌晨5時堂食，只可做外賣。因此不少市民亦加緊購買物資，以減少出外和加強防疫，網上就流傳一張通告，表示超市有臨時限朋措施，對白米、雞蛋、洗手液、口罩等每人限購兩件。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/497756/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E5%A2%9E%E5%8A%A0-%E6%83%A0%E5%BA%B7%E5%85%A8%E7%B7%9A%E6%8C%87%E5%AE%9A%E8%B2%A8%E5%93%81%E9%99%90%E8%B3%BC2%E4%BB%B6-%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E5%A4%A7%E7%B1%B3%E9%9B%9E%E8%9B%8B%E5%BB%81%E7%B4%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F497756%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%259C%2580%25E6%25B1%2582%25E5%25A2%259E%25E5%258A%25A0-%25E6%2583%25A0%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%25B7%259A%25E6%258C%2587%25E5%25AE%259A%25E8%25B2%25A8%25E5%2593%2581%25E9%2599%2590%25E8%25B3%25BC2%25E4%25BB%25B6-%25E5%258C%2585%25E6%258B%25AC%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E7%25B1%25B3%25E9%259B%259E%25E8%259B%258B%25E5%25BB%2581%25E7%25B4%2599&d=nqzd6QM3TLyrPp4uhCfCn5MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=e3ea0e92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/497756/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%9C%80%E6%B1%82%E5%A2